{"word":"βούλησις","slug":"βούλησις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βούλησις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βούλομαι'><el>βούλομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a willing</i>: one's <i>will, intention, purpose</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>the purpose</i> or <i>meaning</i> of a poem, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}